# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# File     : GRND036-dual-rule-unique-rem-policy.ttl
# Domain   : Deontic Ontology / ODRL Grounding
# Problem  : Dual-rule unique rem: same event+rule founds at most one remedy relator
# Refs     : Mohammed et al., What Does ODRL Mean? FOIS 2026
# Generated: 2026-03-26 by gen_foundation_problems.py
# Links    : Discriminating/GRND036-dual-rule-unique-rem-1.p
#            Discriminating/GRND036-dual-rule-unique-rem-1.smt2
